text: Danny Faure (born 8 May 1962) is a Ugandan-born Seychellois politician. He was the 4th President of Seychelles from 16 October 2016 to 26 October 2020. He was Vice President of Seychelles from 2010 to 2016. Faure is a member of the People's Party (PP). ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Seychelles Category:Vice presidents of Seychelles
